# Business Requirements Document (BRD)

## Project Name

Sales Performance Analysis Dashboard

## Business Problem

The organization lacks a centralized reporting solution for monitoring sales performance across products, customers, and geographic regions. Existing reports provide raw transactional data but do not deliver actionable insights for business decision-makers.

## Business Objective

Develop an interactive dashboard that enables stakeholders to:

* Monitor sales performance
* Track profitability
* Identify top-performing products
* Analyze customer behavior
* Support strategic decision-making

## Stakeholders

* Sales Managers
* Regional Managers
* Executive Leadership
* Business Analysts

## Scope

The dashboard will provide:

* Total Sales KPIs
* Profit KPIs
* Regional Performance Analysis
* Product Category Analysis
* Customer Performance Analysis
* Monthly Sales Trends

## Success Criteria

* Dashboard provides real-time business insights.
* Stakeholders can identify sales trends and performance issues.
* Decision-making is supported through visual analytics and reporting.

## Assumptions

* Sales data is accurate and complete.
* Stakeholders have access to Power BI reports.
